类 OSSClientBuilder

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    OSSBuilder

    public class OSSClientBuilder
extends Object
implements OSSBuilder
    Fluent builder for OSS Client. Use of the builder is preferred over using constructors of the client class.

      • build

        public OSS build(String endpoint,
        String accessKeyId,
        String secretAccessKey,
        String securityToken,
        ClientBuilderConfiguration config)
        从接口复制的说明: OSSBuilder
        Uses specified OSS Endpoint, the temporary (Access Id/Access Key/Security Token) from STS and the client configuration to create a new OSSClient instance.
        指定者:
        build 在接口中 OSSBuilder
        参数:
        endpoint - OSS Endpoint.
        accessKeyId - Access Key Id provided by STS.
        secretAccessKey - Secret Access Key provided by STS.
        securityToken - Security token provided by STS.
        config - A ClientBuilderConfiguration instance. The method would use default configuration if it's null.
